This project focuses on performing Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) on a sales dataset to uncover meaningful insights about customer behavior and sales performance. The analysis helps understand how different customer attributes influence purchasing patterns and revenue generation.

The project is implemented using Python and visualized using Matplotlib and Seaborn, making the insights easy to interpret and business-friendly.

